rainbow stripes.<\/p>\n\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/18083&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/23124741\/must-do-peru-south-america.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/23124741\/must-do-peru-south-america-19x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/12\/23124741\/must-do-peru-south-america-376x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"11 Best Things To Do in Peru\" height=\"600\" width=\"376\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a>\n\n\n<p><strong>Good to know: <\/strong>The hike is well worth it but be prepared for the high altitude.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use>