u<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Get the perfect cup of Peruvian coffee from one of the overhanging cafe balconies and try Peru&#x2019;s national dish- Ceviche (Morena is our fave!).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130753\/peru-travel-ceviche-626x810.jpg\" alt=\"peru travel ceviche\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"peru travel ceviche\" data-id=\"17196\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130753\/peru-travel-ceviche.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/travel-blogs\/peru-travel-guide\/attachment\/peru-travel-ceviche\/\" class=\"wp-image-17196 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 626px) 100vw, 626px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130753\/peru-travel-ceviche-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130753\/peru-travel-ceviche-300x388.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130753\/peru-travel-ceviche-600x776.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130753\/peru-travel-ceviche-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130753\/peru-travel-ceviche-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130753\/peru-travel-ceviche-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130753\/peru-travel-ceviche-126x163.jpg 126w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130753\/peru-travel-ceviche-139x180.jpg 139w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130753\/peru-travel-ceviche-594x768.jpg 594w, https:\/\/s