heritage-sites\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">UNESCO World Heritage Site<\/a>. Drawn in the sand in the middle of the desert are more than 70 human and animal geoglyphs, which have been preserved for a span of 2000 years due to the arid conditions. Climb up the viewing tower next to the highway to get an awesome bird&#x2019;s eye perspective!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130736\/peru-travel-guide-nazca-lines.jpg\" alt=\"peru travel guide nazca lines\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"peru travel guide nazca lines\" class=\"wp-image-17203 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130736\/peru-travel-guide-nazca-lines.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130736\/peru-travel-guide-nazca-lines-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130736\/peru-travel-guide-nazca-lines-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130736\/peru-travel-guide-nazca-lines-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130736\/peru-travel-guide-nazca-lines-800x533.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130736\/peru-travel-guide-nazca-lines-1080x720.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130736\/peru-travel-guide-nazca-lines-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130736\/peru-travel-guide-nazca-lines-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/10\/23130736\/peru-travel-guide-nazca-lines-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content